trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for a Web server control <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller en basklass för en webbserverkontrollen <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: WebControlToolboxItem provides a base class for toolbox items that create Web server controls.
trans-unit.target: WebControlToolboxItem innehåller en basklass för objekt i verktygslådan som skapar webbserverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class extends <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> and provides the following additional methods: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolAttributeValue%2A> gets the value of an attribute of the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen utökar <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>och tillhandahåller följande ytterligare metoder:- <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolAttributeValue%2A>hämtar värdet för ett attribut för verktygslådeobjektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolAttributeValue%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolHtml%2A> gets the HTML that represents the initial state of the control.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolHtml%2A>hämtar HTML som representerar inledningsvis i kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolType%2A> gets the type of the associated runtime component.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolType%2A>hämtar typ av associerad runtime-komponent.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolType%2A>
